{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"sdbmhash","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This algorithm was created for sdbm (a public-domain reimplementation of ndbm) database library."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"it was found to do well in scrambling bits, causing better distribution of the keys and fewer splits."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"it also happens to be a good general hashing function with good distribution."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the actual function is hash(i) = hash(i - 1) * 65599 + str[i];"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"what is included below is the faster version used in gawk."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[there is even a faster, duff-device version] the magic prime constant 65599 (2^6 + 2^16 - 1)"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"was picked out of thin air while experimenting with many different constants."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"this is one of the algorithms used in berkeley db (see sleepycat) and elsewhere."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras","doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras\/Swift","doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras\/Swift\/String"]]},"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras\/Swift\/String\/sdbmhash","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Hashed string"}],"metadata":{"extendedModule":"Swift","title":"sdbmhash","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"property","roleHeading":"Instance Property","externalID":"s:SS11SwiftExtrasE8sdbmhashSivp","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"sdbmhash","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"SwiftExtras","relatedModules":["Swift"]}]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/swiftextras\/swift\/string\/sdbmhash"]}],"references":{"doc://SwiftExtras/documentation/SwiftExtras/Swift":{"type":"topic","title":"Swift","url":"\/documentation\/swiftextras\/swift","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras\/Swift"},"doc://SwiftExtras/documentation/SwiftExtras/Swift/String":{"title":"String","abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/swiftextras\/swift\/string","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"String","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras\/Swift\/String","fragments":[{"text":"extension","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"String","kind":"identifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"}]},"doc://SwiftExtras/documentation/SwiftExtras/Swift/String/sdbmhash":{"title":"sdbmhash","url":"\/documentation\/swiftextras\/swift\/string\/sdbmhash","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras\/Swift\/String\/sdbmhash","type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"sdbmhash","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Hashed string","type":"text"}]},"doc://SwiftExtras/documentation/SwiftExtras":{"abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/